&lt;div class="_46-h _5pc3" style="width: 398px; height: 223px;"&gt;&lt;img class="_46-i img" src="https://fbcdn-sphotos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-ash4/t1/p75x225/1797347_752861774725053_316263386_n.jpg" height="225" alt="Está disponível o LibreOffice 4.2.2 RC1 para testes.
